### Solo SaaS — API 接口测试
### 安装 REST Client 插件后，点击 "Send Request" 直接测试
### 变量：在 .env.local 中设置 BASE_URL=http://localhost:3000

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@contentType = application/json
@token = YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

# ─────────────────────────────────────────
# 健康检查
# ─────────────────────────────────────────

### GET 健康检查
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/health HTTP/1.1

###

# ─────────────────────────────────────────
# 认证
# ─────────────────────────────────────────

### POST 注册 / 登录（Magic Link）
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/signin HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "callbackUrl": "{{baseUrl}}/dashboard"
}

###

### GET 获取当前会话
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/session HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

# ─────────────────────────────────────────
# 用户
# ─────────────────────────────────────────

### GET 获取当前用户信息
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/user/me HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### PATCH 更新用户信息
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/user/me HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "张三",
  "avatarUrl": "https://example.com/avatar.png"
}

###

# ─────────────────────────────────────────
# 组织
# ─────────────────────────────────────────

### POST 创建组织
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/organizations HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "我的公司",
  "slug": "my-company"
}

###

### GET 获取组织列表
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/organizations HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### POST 邀请成员
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/organizations/my-company/members HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "email": "colleague@example.com",
  "role": "MEMBER"
}

###

# ─────────────────────────────────────────
# 订阅 / 计费
# ─────────────────────────────────────────

### POST 创建 Stripe Checkout Session
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/billing/checkout HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "priceId": "price_xxxxx",
  "successUrl": "{{baseUrl}}/dashboard?success=1",
  "cancelUrl": "{{baseUrl}}/pricing"
}

###

### GET 获取订阅状态
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/billing/subscription HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### POST Stripe Webhook（本地测试用 stripe listen --forward-to localhost:3000/api/billing/webhook）
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/billing/webhook HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Stripe-Signature: t=xxx,v1=xxx

{
  "type": "checkout.session.completed",
  "data": { "object": {} }
}

###
